<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
      <title>Admin Home - Engineered Assets</title>
      <meta name="description" content="Manage users, engineering tools, orders, and carts seamlessly.">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/bootstrap.min.css" />
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css" />
      <script src="/js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
      <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
      <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
      <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #D8D2C2; 
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .center {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .section h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Navbar link styles */
        .navbar-inverse .nav > li > a {
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-inverse .nav > li > a:hover {
            color: #ffd700; /* Gold hover effect */
        }

        /* Navbar brand (Engineering Assets) */
        .navbar-inverse .navbar-brand {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px; /* Larger font size */
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-inverse .navbar-brand:hover {
            color: #ffd700; /* Gold hover effect */
        }

        .navbar-inverse .nav i {
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .navbar-inverse {
            background-color: #343a40;
            border: none;
        }
      </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
        <a class="navbar-brand">Engineering Assets</a>
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li><a href="/adminHomepage"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Admin Home Page</a></li>
          <li><a href="/profile"><i class="fas fa-user-cog"></i> Profile Management</a></li>
          <li><a href="/Equipments"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Equipments Management</a></li>
          <li><a href="/AddEquipments"><i class="fas fa-plus-square"></i> Add Equipment</a></li>
          <li><a href="/admincart"><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> Cart</a></li>
          <li><a href="/adminorder"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Orders</a></li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right" style="padding-right: 30px;">
          <li><a href="/"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="center">
      <h1>Welcome, Admin {{ name }}</h1>
      <p>Manage your profile, explore our equipment inventory, track orders, and manage your cart for a seamless experience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Users Management</h2>
      <p>Manage user accounts and details to ensure a smooth experience. <a href="/profile">Visit the users management page</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Explore Equipments</h2>
      <p>Discover a wide range of engineering tools and assets, categorized for easy browsing. <a href="/Equipments">Browse Equipments</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Review Your Cart</h2>
      <p>Ensure everything is ready before checkout. Adjust quantities, remove items, or proceed to purchase. <a href="/admincart">View your cart</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Track Your Orders</h2>
      <p>Stay informed about the status of placed orders, including current stages and estimated delivery times. <a href="/adminorder">Check your orders</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>